{"id":314749,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-浙江冤妇陆冬菜在黑监狱被囚一年半又进/","date":"2013-09-23T05:34:30Z","modified":"2013-09-23T05:34:30Z","title":"维权网 | 浙江冤妇陆冬菜在黑监狱被囚一年半又进久敬庄（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员黄天怒报道）浙江省天台县赤城街道九峰村农妇陆冬菜，因</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年丈夫被摩托车撞死得不到公正处理而上访，儿子因她上访先后被两所学校赶出而沦为囚犯，她自己因上访两次被刑事拘留、三次行政拘留、四次送精神病医院、判刑坐牢一年半、多次被关黑监狱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>自去年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月初到今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月初，陆冬菜在浙江当地的黑监狱一直被关了一年半，过着与世隔绝的生活。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日陆冬菜从黑监狱出来后，稍事休息，又马不停蹄地赴京诉冤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日下午，陆冬菜在北京信访，再次被送进中国最大的黑监狱——久敬庄关押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陆冬菜电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15268864455</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-bj4lMWD6QxM/Uj_MqPrSD1I/AAAAAAAAogo/WlmGcGuRx9Y/s1600/IMG_1269.JPG2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"222\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-bj4lMWD6QxM/Uj_MqPrSD1I/AAAAAAAAogo/WlmGcGuRx9Y/s320/IMG_1269.JPG2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-KEnrCaXIPlE/Uj_MtjhFzRI/AAAAAAAAogw/IstArwMDkg0/s1600/img333.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-KEnrCaXIPlE/Uj_MtjhFzRI/AAAAAAAAogw/IstArwMDkg0/s320/img333.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-YT0Uh9o4fEI/Uj_MytI-bEI/AAAAAAAAohA/lS-dxI9z7Sw/s1600/img334.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-YT0Uh9o4fEI/Uj_MytI-bEI/AAAAAAAAohA/lS-dxI9z7S